    <item>
      <title>Font Awesome - Excelente para designers.</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/general/font-awesome-excelente-para-designers</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Oct 2014 10:56:42 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/general/font-awesome-excelente-para-designers</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;Nós, aqui, temos uma categoria unicamente dedicada a ferramentas para desenvolvedores e, hoje, trazemos mais um item para ser colocado nessa categoria.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Apesar de não ser uma ferramenta de definição, colocarei este artigo nessa categoria porque a &lt;strong&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/strong&gt; é algo que pode ser deveras útil para os programadores e &lt;em&gt;web designers&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/fontawesome.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Font Awesome - Excelente para designers.&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/strong&gt; é um projeto &lt;em&gt;open source&lt;/em&gt; que nos permite, de forma muito simples, incorporar ícones em páginas &lt;em&gt;web&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Como assim? Através de um simples ficheiro CSS temos à nossa disposição uma gigante quantidade de ícones padrão como o símbolo de eliminar, câmara, de redes sociais, etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;como-instalar:409e4fee0e71fc53e6c8d129bdfedc19&#34;&gt;Como &amp;ldquo;instalar&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Existem diversas formas de utilizar a &lt;em&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/em&gt;. A primeira e mais fácil forma é, simplesmente, chamar o ficheiro CSS da fonte no cabeçalho de um ficheiro HTML.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;link&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;href=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;rel=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;stylesheet&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Pode também descarregar os ficheiros da &lt;em&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/&#34;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt; e chamar o ficheiro CSS principal, o font-awesome.min.css font-awesome.min.css  através do HTML.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Existem outras formas mais complicadas que podem ser úteis em diversas situações. Pode ver &lt;a href=&#34;http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/get-started/&#34;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt; mais formas de instalar a &lt;em&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;como-utilizar:409e4fee0e71fc53e6c8d129bdfedc19&#34;&gt;Como utilizar&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A utilização da Font Awesomeé deveras simples. Para inserir ícones utilizamos a seguinte sintaxe:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;fa fa-nome fa-tamanho&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;No código HTML acima devemos substituir nome  pelo respetivo nome do ícone que pode encontrar &lt;a href=&#34;http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/&#34;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt; e, tamanho  por um dos seguintes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/fontawesomesize.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;fontawesomesize&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Existem ainda muitos outros atributos que pode adicionar ao código de forma a personalizar o ícone. Veja a tabela seguinte:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Código&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Para que serve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;

&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;fa-spin&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Faz com que o ícone rode continuamente no sentido dos ponteiros do relógio.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;fa-border&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Adiciona uma borda ao ícone.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;fa-rotate-x&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Gira o ícone 90, 180 ou 270 graus (colocar os graus em vez de &amp;ldquo;x&amp;rdquo;).&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;fa-flip-x&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Transforma o ícone no seu simétrico vertical ou horizontalmente.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Etc&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Pode ver mais &lt;a href=&#34;http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/examples/&#34;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Como pode ver, este pequeno CSS pode ser extremamente útil quando o site/aplicação que está a desenvolver necessita de muitos ícones. Se quiser ler mais sobre a Font Awesome, pode aceder ao seu site oficial &lt;a href=&#34;http://fontawesome.io/&#34;&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>SASS - Será a futura versão do CSS?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/personal/sass-sera-a-futura-versao-do-css</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Sep 2014 10:23:57 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/personal/sass-sera-a-futura-versao-do-css</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Atualmente, uma das grandes vertentes da programação é a web e esta está muito difundida. Os desenvolvedores web, têm que utilizar várias linguagens de vários tipos: programação, marcação e estilo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A última versão do CSS &lt;em&gt;(Cascading Style Sheet)&lt;/em&gt;, o CSS3, trouxe muitas melhorias e novidades tornando-se mais poderoso. &lt;strong&gt;Mas será suficiente?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/sass.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;SASS - Será a futura versão do CSS?&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Atualmente, existem várias &amp;ldquo;alternativas&amp;rdquo; e pré-processadores de CSS, como &lt;a href=&#34;http://lesscss.org/&#34;&gt;LESS&lt;/a&gt; e SASS. Este último, tem vindo a crescer e muitos acreditam que poderá ser a &lt;strong&gt;futura versão do CSS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;O SASS está na versão 3.4.3 e toda a versão três é mais conhecida por SCSS ou seja, Sassy CSS. Para utilizar esta ferramenta é necessário terem Ruby instalado no vosso computador. Pode seguir as restantes &lt;a href=&#34;http://sass-lang.com/install&#34;&gt;instruções aqui&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Aqui está um pequeno exemplo que compara CSS com SCSS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cm&#34;&gt;/* CSS */&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;nav&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;blue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;font-family&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;sans-serif&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;nav&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;ul&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;list-style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;


&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;nav&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;li&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;inline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;nav&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;text-decoration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;red&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;//O Mesmo em SCSS&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;$font-stack&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;sans-serif&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;$primary-color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;blue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;$links-color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;red&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;nav&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$primary-color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;font-family&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$font-stack&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;ul&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;list-style&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;li&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;inline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;text-decoration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;no&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nv&#34;&gt;$links-color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Sim, viram bem. Com SCSS podemos utilizar variáveis e também aninhar itens. Mas não acaba por aqui. Existem várias outras funcionalidades:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Importar ficheiros com &lt;code&gt;@import &#39;nome&#39;&lt;/code&gt;;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mixins;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Herança utilizando &lt;code&gt;@extend&lt;/code&gt;;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operadores aritméticos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Podem ler mais sobre estas funcionalidades no &lt;a href=&#34;http://sass-lang.com/guide&#34;&gt;guia oficial&lt;/a&gt;. Uma das grandes vantagens em utilizar este pré-processador é o aumento de produtividade.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Agora, deixo-vos a pergunta: acham que o SCSS pode vir a ser o futuro CSS?
Poder-se-à tornar mais que um pré-processador?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
</description>
